inventarium (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * Product hierarchy management (Products, Packages, Batches, Labels)
  * Barcode generation with code128
  * Expiration tracking with FEFO management
  * Multi-language support (Italian, English, Spanish)
  * SQLite database backend

